017c35b9-7088-4b35-899c-ed82606dfdd7.title: Note
017c35b9-7088-4b35-899c-ed82606dfdd7.text: forgot to talk to Omad again after agreeing to find Cedric.

edcd9bac-100c-45aa-9b28-7759e53ba1db.title: Note
edcd9bac-100c-45aa-9b28-7759e53ba1db.text: forgot to talk to Omad after talking to Cedric/before giving them water.

495b125c-85db-4208-8792-40c0dbd86916.title: Brother Omad
495b125c-85db-4208-8792-40c0dbd86916.text:
*yawn*...oh, hello...*yawn* I'm sorry! I'm just so tired!
I haven't slept in a week!

options.text: 遰 Why can't you sleep, what's wrong?
Sorry! I'm too busy to hear your problems!

7e3cfedc-95b7-4cf9-996b-d4c0e3af9925.title: <player>
7e3cfedc-95b7-4cf9-996b-d4c0e3af9925.text: Sorry! I'm too busy to hear your problems!

ba6041c1-bc4d-4ed4-921e-166dc3656984.title: <player>
ba6041c1-bc4d-4ed4-921e-166dc3656984.text: Why can't you sleep, what's wrong?

9719005c-e787-4cbd-88a8-87a221d10366.title: Brother Omad
9719005c-e787-4cbd-88a8-87a221d10366.text:
It's brother Androe's son! With his constant: Waaaaaah!
Waaaaaaaaah! Androe said it's natural, but it's so
annoying!

392baeea-aa63-429c-8a71-8ab392a5efdd.title: <player>
392baeea-aa63-429c-8a71-8ab392a5efdd.text: I suppose that's what kids do.

06baff99-a0b6-4525-93db-cc9d07b35591.title: Brother Omad
06baff99-a0b6-4525-93db-cc9d07b35591.text:
He was fine, up until last week! Thieves broke in! They
stole his favourite sleeping blanket!

399f02c7-7af5-4c47-ae74-ae7699b88923.title: Brother Omad
399f02c7-7af5-4c47-ae74-ae7699b88923.text:
Now he won't rest until it's returned... ...and that
means neither can I!

07003714-c775-498f-ab94-62467d5c3c8b.title: <player>
07003714-c775-498f-ab94-62467d5c3c8b.text: I'm sorry to hear that! I hope you find his blanket.

9139a6ab-79a5-4f3c-bd12-71f68eff06cd.title: Brother Omad
9139a6ab-79a5-4f3c-bd12-71f68eff06cd.text:
Please do. We won't be able to help you as we are
peaceful men but we would be grateful for your help!

3cf338d3-e817-4b8c-957a-abde62d0349e.title: Brother Omad
3cf338d3-e817-4b8c-957a-abde62d0349e.text:
They hide in a secret cave in the forest. It's hidden
under a ring of stones. Please, bring back the blanket!

da5ad592-0994-4613-96c3-c53108d83199.title: Brother Omad
da5ad592-0994-4613-96c3-c53108d83199.text: Please tell me you have the blanket.

49032081-4be2-400f-9054-ec470d063b17.title: Brother Omad
49032081-4be2-400f-9054-ec470d063b17.text: Please tell me you have the blanket.

6c55db2f-722a-4024-acdc-9d4ec35f3707.title: <player>
6c55db2f-722a-4024-acdc-9d4ec35f3707.text:
Yes! I've recovered it from the clutches of the evil
thieves!

fcae4be2-9bbc-4162-b79e-6b104e83cf46.text: You hand the monk the childs blanket.

e5c836b5-2314-4496-a237-03c23c954c0a.title: Brother Omad
e5c836b5-2314-4496-a237-03c23c954c0a.text:
Really, that's excellent, well done! Maybe now I will be
able to get some rest.

0d54cf16-10d0-4f46-874c-916e5f875e2d.title: Brother Omad
0d54cf16-10d0-4f46-874c-916e5f875e2d.text: *yawn*..I'm off to bed! Farewell brave traveller!

f7c89150-0175-4f03-aeda-5ea090fcc5ba.title: Brother Omad
f7c89150-0175-4f03-aeda-5ea090fcc5ba.text:
Much better now I'm sleeping well! Now I can organise
the party.

6275eea0-95ea-4c49-8512-f75d6682de60.title: Brother Omad
6275eea0-95ea-4c49-8512-f75d6682de60.text:
The son of Brother Androe's birthday party. He's going
to be one year old!

d30d8086-9f1f-4878-8ab1-d3265b13de97.title: Brother Omad
d30d8086-9f1f-4878-8ab1-d3265b13de97.text: It's also a great excuse for a drink!

044cbf00-597f-49b9-bdfc-5ea32c40edc4.title: Brother Omad
044cbf00-597f-49b9-bdfc-5ea32c40edc4.text: We just need Brother Cedric to return with the wine.

options.text: Enjoy it! I'll see you soon!

2bd4f294-44cd-4f97-a454-84d534b3db8a.title: <player>
2bd4f294-44cd-4f97-a454-84d534b3db8a.text: Enjoy it! I'll see you soon!

c1ed80ee-9c3a-4c40-ad7b-5a5284696f97.title: Brother Omad
c1ed80ee-9c3a-4c40-ad7b-5a5284696f97.text:
Cedric is a member of the order too. We sent him out
three days ago to collect wine. But he didn't return!

ac3857c8-4086-421a-ad33-edc2391b99b9.title: Brother Omad
ac3857c8-4086-421a-ad33-edc2391b99b9.text: He most probably got drunk and lost in the forest!

2c28c189-6656-48ff-b024-8d5501328197.title: Brother Omad
2c28c189-6656-48ff-b024-8d5501328197.text: I don't suppose you could look for him?

options.text: I've no time for that, sorry.
Can I come to the party?

52ffa2fc-409d-4133-aaf6-9eed54804a4e.title: <player>
52ffa2fc-409d-4133-aaf6-9eed54804a4e.text: I've no time for that, sorry.

3c755965-d314-47f4-a020-996ed54d4c45.title: <player>
3c755965-d314-47f4-a020-996ed54d4c45.text: Can I come to the party?

a383ba50-e16c-46e6-b4b1-078f07cca648.title: Brother Omad
a383ba50-e16c-46e6-b4b1-078f07cca648.text: Of course, but we need the wine first.

9c7d5907-f1eb-4287-839c-434f8e67e554.title: Brother Omad
9c7d5907-f1eb-4287-839c-434f8e67e554.text: Oh, he won't be far. Probably out in the forest.

2bfa077c-ddd3-4961-8af9-6d90a3b60d7d.title: <player>
2bfa077c-ddd3-4961-8af9-6d90a3b60d7d.text: Ok, I'll go and find him.

ad0caedb-1537-4b3c-ad8b-52a6ea301549.title: <player>
ad0caedb-1537-4b3c-ad8b-52a6ea301549.text: He's having a bit of trouble with his cart.

c7f5b680-21b7-4be4-8f4e-e541da258aee.title: <player>
c7f5b680-21b7-4be4-8f4e-e541da258aee.text: Hi Omad, Brother Cedric is on his way!

1bb54d39-6abc-49f3-aca7-cd0dc93be46d.title: Brother Omad
1bb54d39-6abc-49f3-aca7-cd0dc93be46d.text: Good! Good! Now we can party!

80ead829-bb4b-403f-83a8-bc81cb731fcb.title: Brother Omad
80ead829-bb4b-403f-83a8-bc81cb731fcb.text:
I have little to repay you with but please, take these
runes.

b2c880d8-66ce-4259-9c00-a7d648797ad3.text: Brother Omad gives you 8 Law Runes.

d1d58b1b-1a8d-4774-91ed-b77430112edd.title: Note
d1d58b1b-1a8d-4774-91ed-b77430112edd.text:
Quest comeplete!
1 QP
2k Woodcutting XP
8 Law Runes

d0faaa9b-1680-4c2d-85ab-65262831366f.title: Brother Omad
d0faaa9b-1680-4c2d-85ab-65262831366f.text: Dum dee do la la! *hiccup* That was some party!
